| AsyncBenchmarks<Matrix4x4> | NewAsync | False   |  46.21 ns | 0.052 ns |  0.046 ns |   1,658 B |         - |
|                            |          |         |           |          |           |           |           |
| AsyncBenchmarks<Matrix4x4> | OldAsync | True    | 417.52 ns | 1.514 ns |  1.416 ns |   3,217 B |     344 B |
| AsyncBenchmarks<Matrix4x4> | NewAsync | True    | 398.02 ns | 3.560 ns |  2.972 ns |   4,094 B |     272 B |
|                            |          |         |           |          |           |           |           |
| AsyncBenchmarks<Object>    | OldAsync | False   |  33.96 ns | 0.393 ns |  0.368 ns |     733 B |         - |
| AsyncBenchmarks<Object>    | NewAsync | False   |  35.82 ns | 0.514 ns |  0.456 ns |     640 B |         - |
